  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The use of a render finish on the proposed additional storey on the rear extension, rather than facing brick, would draw unwarranted attention to the additional bulk, & depart from the overall character of the terrace of which the property forms part. The proposal conflicts with Policies D4 & D11 of Islington's UDP 2002, which require alterations & extensions to be sympathetic to the surrounding buildings, & to respect the architectural character & detail of the original building itself, & fails to respect the principles of sympathetic use of materials & detailing set out in Section 2.5 of the Islington Urban Design Guidelines of December 2006."
